@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.75 * tmp + 0.09) / (v1 + 0.21 - tmp + 0.19)))
    v1 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(tmp + 0.88) - (tmp + 0.46 / tmp + 0.42)))
    v0 = 0.73
    tmp = (wp.exp(v0) * wp.abs((v2 + 0.13 - tmp + 0.39)))
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.15)) / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
